  <brief_title>Impact of a Low Carbohydrate Breakfast on Glucose Control in Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Impact of a Low Carbohydrate Breakfast on Glucose Control in Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
